Package: snowcat
Type: Package
Title: SNOWCAT: GWAS with Local Ancestry Correction
Version: 0.9
Date: 2021-09-08
Authors@R: c(person("Andrey A", "Shabalin",
                    role = c("aut", "cre"),
                    email = "andrey.shabalin@gmail.com",
                    comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0309-6821")))
Maintainer: Andrey A Shabalin <andrey.shabalin@gmail.com>
Description: A complete toolset for
        genome-wide association studies 
        with variant-wise correction for ancestry
        as estimated with RFMIX.
        It follows the model originally introduced by
        Elizabeth G. Atkinson in the TRACTOR pipeline.
URL: https://github.com/andreyshabalin/snowcat/
BugReports: https://github.com/andreyshabalin/snowcat/issues
License: LGPL-3
LazyLoad: yes
NeedsCompilation: no
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0), filematrix
Imports: stats, utils, data.table, parallel

